# Problem Set 02: Bank Marketing Prediction Using Logistic Regression

## Overview

This project focuses on predicting whether a bank customer will subscribe to a term deposit or not based on their demographic and banking information.  
We use a *Logistic Regression model*, a common classification algorithm suitable for binary outcomes.

---

## Dataset

- The dataset contains information about bank customers including:
  - *Demographics:* Age, Job, Marital Status, Education
  - *Financial Info:* Balance, Default, Housing Loan, Personal Loan
  - *Target:* Whether the customer subscribed to a term deposit (y column: yes/no)

- *In this implementation, a **synthetic dataset* is generated with the same structure as the real bank dataset.  
- You can replace the synthetic CSV with your real dataset by changing the dataset_url in the code.

